### Register user
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "mobile": "9998887776",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "Admin"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Check auth
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/check-auth

### Get profile
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/profile

### Update profile
PUT http://localhost:4000/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name"
}

### Change password
PUT http://localhost:4000/auth/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "secret123",
  "newPassword": "newSecret123"
}

### Logout
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/logout
